tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE quantum_simulation (
    simulation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_name VARCHAR(50),
    qubits_used INT,
    gate_operations VARCHAR(100),
    execution_time DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE visualization_data (
    visualization_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    simulation_id INT REFERENCES quantum_simulation(simulation_id),
    visualization_type VARCHAR(50),
    visual_data BYTEA,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE ExperimentResults (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_id INT,
    quantum_result JSON,
    result_time TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (experiment_id) REFERENCES ExperimentData(experiment_id)
);

CREATE TABLE VisualizationData (
    vis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_id INT,
    visualization_type TEXT,
    visualization_data JSON,
    FOREIGN KEY (experiment_id) REFERENCES ExperimentData(experiment_id)
);

CREATE TABLE ExperimentLogs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_id INT,
    log_message TEXT,
    log_time TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (experiment_id) REFERENCES ExperimentData(experiment_id)
);
